{"tid":614872,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 熊市定調整","createTime":"2018-04-03T02:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T10:14:39.000Z","uid":90595,"like":70,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c9e1f326aa30254b32a2017ace4899e52b903d","tid":614872,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"利申左先，我係淡友<br />\n壞消息同睇跌嘅原因就唔list啦，多不勝數<br />\n今非昔比，但發覺仍然有唔少人睇升<br />\n但我思前想後，好友到底呢排諗緊乜呢？<br />\n睇升嘅原因？就係跌落去時做嘅反彈<br />\n最好笑係覺得trump trump會唔打貿易戰，唔打就會升番上去<br />\n而最大嘅好消息，就係夠鐘收市同假期<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇？<br />\n熊市，正評<br />\n調整/大調整，負評"},{"pid":"c8438c0ce667360d3047d18d87ef31c30770c069","tid":614872,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"50-50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a51f276950600ec34d2819b3cddcb9309f0a00c","tid":614872,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"家下好明顯係牛三"},{"pid":"b4027281dd6bc451c2a56910a2d3b75edabc9291","tid":614872,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"大戶震倉呃貨"},{"pid":"a7a2929337a2cd4208b8e0837e9c58a1751faa94","tid":614872,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50-50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 打電話問大師"},{"pid":"03a99c18b9042cb4726b013967078c08dd00e